      "span_id": "p040_s0001",
      "text": "INCITS xxx-200x Link Services Rev 1.61 November 3, 2006",
      "bbox": [
        301.08,
        37.27,
        539.95,
        47.32
      ],
      "block_index": 1,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0002",
      "text": " 21",
      "bbox": [
        521.04,
        723.59,
        534.92,
        734.7
      ],
      "block_index": 2,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0003",
      "text": "An ELS Protocol is composed of an ELS request Sequence and, for some requests, an ELS Reply",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        429.65,
        539.98,
        440.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0004",
      "text": "Sequence.  The last Data frame of an ELS request Sequence with a Reply Sequence shall transfer",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        441.65,
        539.93,
        452.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0005",
      "text": "the Sequence Initiative to the Recipient in order to allow the reply to be transmitted (see FC-FS-2). If",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        453.65,
        539.95,
        464.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0006",
      "text": "an ELS request Sequence that has a Reply Sequence is transmitted without the transfer of Se-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        465.65,
        540.24,
        476.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0007",
      "text": "quence Initiative, the Recipient shall abort the Exchange and not perform the request. ",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        477.65,
        476.48,
        488.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0008",
      "text": "The following ELS requests and their replies shall be supported by an Nx_Port (all others are optional",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.97,
        540.05,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 4,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p040_s0009",
      "text": "for purposes of this standard, other standards or Technical Reports may require further ELS support):",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.97,
